dataItem-j73rd1t4.text: Tap the app, your food & drink is ready

dataItem-j73rd1tg.text: One tap and your food & drink is ready - no calling ahead or waiting in queues. Just walk in, pick up and walk out. And payment is completely cashless.

dataItem-j73rd1un.text: AtHand works with your favourite restaurants. We believe that awesome food should be effortlessly available to pick up.

dataItem-j73rd1uw.text: Your favourite restaurants in one app

dataItem-j73rd1vz.text: Breakfast, lunch or dinner. Morning or afternoon coffee. Whatever you're picking up, always count on AtHand for your food & drink.

dataItem-j73rd1w9.text: Choose from your favourite restaurants

dataItem-j73rd1wn.text: Get your food & drink in seconds, whether you're picking up breakfast, lunch or dinner.

dataItem-j77h1kv0.text: "Why can't you just push a button and your food & drink is ready?" AtHand began as the answer to that simple question.

dataItem-j797186f.text: Your Food & Drink Remote Control

dataItem-j7yjqyfn.text: Keep tuned as we announce our incredible partner restaurants!
